dc_description_s: Map in 4 sheets is put together as 1. Oriented to northwest. On recto: Map of Habana on sheets marked 1-4 showing roads, water features, built-up areas, facilities of intersest, monuments, schools, stations, and hospitals. On verso: Images with text and key in English, Spanish, French, and Arabic. Ancillary maps of Santa Fé, Rancho Boyeros, Cojimar and Alamar, and Cotorro marked 1a-4a.
dc_creator_sm: Cuba. Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, issuing body
dc_publisher_s: Havana, Cuba : Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, [1980].
